<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>A robber has been captured stealing a woman's phone as she walked along a street with a young girl in Leeds.</p>

<p>CCTV footage showed a man sneak up behind the woman, 15, before grabbing her in Harehills on September 5 around 2.45pm, according to reports.  </p>

<p>He managed to snatch her mobile phone before running away.</p>

<p>CCTV footage showed a man sneak up behind the woman, 15, before grabbing her in Harehills on September 5 around 2.45pm, according to reports</p>

<p>The victim dropped a bag of shopping as she ran after the man, leaving the young girl waiting at the corner of the street. </p>

<p>It was reported online that members of the public later managed to identify and trace the suspect.</p>

<p>His landlord was allegedly informed of the robbery and the thief was subsequently evicted from his home along with his family, reports claimed.</p>

<p>This has not been confirmed.  </p>

